thc-ipv6 (2.0-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * New upstream release (closes: #690520).
  * Move to 3.0 (quilt) format.
  * Bump compat level to 7.
  * Bumb Standard Version to 3.9.3.
  * Adjusted the Makefile to fix prefix path.
  * Adjusted the Makefile to remove language extension from scripts.
  * Fix dos_mld syntax check.
  * Build with hardening options.
  * Disable linking against OpenSSL because a link exemption is not
    yet available.

